---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<section id="contacto">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="s-label reveal">Contacto</p>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h2 class="contact-heading">¿Construimos<br /><em>algo juntos?</em></h2>
        <p>
          Estoy abierto a posiciones de backend, distributed systems y
          platform engineering, ya sea remoto o híbrido. También disponible
          para consultoría técnica y colaboraciones en proyectos open-source.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:alex@example.com" class="btn-primary contact-cta">
          Enviar mensaje ↗
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-links reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <a href="mailto:alex@example.com" class="contact-row">
          <div class="contact-row-left">
            <span class="contact-type mono">Email</span>
            <span class="contact-val">alex@example.com</span>
          </div>
          <span class="contact-arrow">↗</span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-row">
          <div class="contact-row-left">
            <span class="contact-type mono">GitHub</span>
            <span class="contact-val">github.com/alexram</span>
          </div>
          <span class="contact-arrow">↗</span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-row">
          <div class="contact-row-left">
            <span class="contact-type mono">LinkedIn</span>
            <span class="contact-val">linkedin.com/in/alexram</span>
          </div>
          <span class="contact-arrow">↗</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/cv.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-row">
          <div class="contact-row-left">
            <span class="contact-type mono">Currículum</span>
            <span class="contact-val">Descargar CV (PDF)</span>
          </div>
          <span class="contact-arrow">↗</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="site-footer reveal">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <span class="mono footer-copy">
          © {year} Jose Ozuna · Software Engineer · Chiapas
        </span>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="#hero" class="mono footer-back">↑ Volver arriba</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .contact-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .contact-heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .contact-grid > div > p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 44ch;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-cta { display: inline-flex; }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--subtle);
  }

  .contact-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--subtle);
    transition: padding-left var(--transition), background var(--transition);
    border-radius: 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .contact-row::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: scaleY(0);
    transition: transform var(--transition);
  }
  .contact-row:hover {
    padding-left: 1rem;
    background: var(--accent-glow2);
  }
  .contact-row:hover::before { transform: scaleY(1); }
  .contact-row:hover .contact-arrow {
    color: var(--accent);
    transform: translate(2px, -2px);
  }

  .contact-row-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .contact-type {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .contact-val { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text); }

  .contact-arrow {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    transition: color var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
  }

  /* Footer */
  .site-footer {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--subtle);
  }

  .footer-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .footer-back {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }
  .footer-back:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>